    "translationText": "Then happiness, and flowers, and Garden of Delights."
  },
  {
    "surahId": 56,
    "ayahNumber": 90,
    "arabicText": "وَأَمَّآ إِن كَانَ مِنْ أَصْحَٰبِ ٱلْيَمِينِ",
    "translationText": "And if he is one of those on the Right."
